FruitieX' Linux dotfiles
------------------------

Install:
--------
1: Run ./firstrun.sh (only if you don't have oh-my-zsh yet)
2: Run ./symlink.sh
3: Enjoy!

Update:
-------
1: git pull
2: Run ./symlink.sh

Dependencies for arch linux users:
----------------------------------
* for script:
pacman -S git curl

* vim:
pacman -S gvim vim-colorsamplerpack vimpager ctags

* wm stuff:
pacman -S i3 i3status dmenu

* misc cli:
pacman -S openssh sudo tmux cmus sshfs ntp terminus-font weechat

* misc gui:
pacman -S rxvt-unicode numlockx redshift feh dwb synergy

* xorg:
pacman -S xorg-server xorg-xset xorg-xsetroot xorg-xmodmap xorg-xinit slim \
archlinux-themes-slim
